{
  "stem": "5255.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were shooting down into the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the third week of September in 1939.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that where my tragedy happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, there was an artillery shell, fell into the building that we lived in on the first floor, sending down the floor completely into the basement.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all my family, and many other neighbors, were in the basement as a-- in the-- at night, because they told us to go into the basement because they were bombarding it from airplanes.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the bombardment was not from airplanes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were from artillery.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they sent down the floor, and as a result my parents, and one my brothers, plus-- including many members of my family, totalling 17 people of my family-- got killed in that particular basement.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But my grandmother that was also in that basement was not killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the reason was-- she was in a pocket where she could get air.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The most of the people died because of lack of air.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They suffocated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my brother and I were in the third floor of the building, that where we lived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we didn't even know that because there was no explosion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we got down early in the morning, about 6 o'clock, the neighbors that were not affected did not want to believe that we were not with our parents, and told us what happened.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were in charge of digging out the people from the basement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were putting them all on the-- on the yard-- on the courtyard of the building.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And two of my uncles survived, my mother's two brothers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother and I.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But four men.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
